100
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,160
Your Majesty.

101
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:35,279
I'm here. Summon an imperial physician.

102
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,319
Your Majesty.

103
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:45,000
